edu.iastate.ansci.flip

Class Breed

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.Breed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Changeable, java.io.Serializable

    public class Breed
extends java.lang.Object
implements Changeable, java.io.Serializable
    Essentialy just a string that notifies listeners when its value changes. Allows for allele frequencies to vary by breed, without worrying about what to do if the breed's name is modified.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
